a.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SJEV/111%2c%e9%87%8d%e5%b0%8f%2c1075%2c20220530%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SJEV,111,重小,1075,20220530,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"重小","JNO":"1075","JDATE":"20220530","JTITLE":"侵權行為損害賠償"}